[30;1m31 | [0m[35m     - Shift/copy children of from-node and remove intermediate parent node[0m
[30;1m32 | [0m[35m     - False (children are not merged)[0m
[30;1m33 | [0m[35m   * - `merge_leaves`[0m
[30;1m34 | [0m[35m     - Shift/copy leaves of from-node and remove all intermediate nodes[0m
[30;1m35 | [0m[35m     - False (leaves are not merged)[0m

[30;1m12 | [0m[35m2. Modify from the Reingold Tilford algorithm from (1)[0m

[30;1m14 | [0m[35m[0m
